Description:

The home consists of a comfortable lounge with separate sunroom, open kitchen meals area, 4 bedrooms and central family bathroom. The garden is a real feature behind the private tree lined nature strip plus the backyard offers an inground pool. The home is privately located only a short walk to the main street shops and schools and just a stroll over the creek to the park. Description:
Modern Retreat On 7.4 Acres
(130 Kirk Road is best accessed off Rainy Hill Road) Set on a private and picturesque 7.4 acres, this stunning double storey sandstone look home, is perfect for those looking to relax and enjoy the beauty that only the hills has to offer.
Stylishly appointed, the home offers a luxurious lifestyle, featuring multiple living areas that include a formal dining area, cosy lounge, and large open plan family and meals area that adjoin the quality kitchen, offering quality stainless steel appliances, including a dishwasher and 900mm oven and cooktop.
Special features include soaring high ceilings, polished concrete floors, quality carpets, fresh modern colour scheme, 2 split system heating and cooling units, wood heater, solar panels to reduce those unwanted bills,
plenty of storage, and large windows that allow plenty of natural light to flow though the home.
Also on offer are 3 bedrooms, a large study, master retreat that offers a stunning ensuite and private balcony, oversized single garage, workshop under roof line and a large covered decked entertaining area that is a great place to sit back and relax. Outside the low maintenance park like setting has plenty of room for you to enjoy. Call today, inspection is a must.

Description:
Gorgeous Country Home on Over 6.5 Acres!
This sun drenched property offers the lifestyle families leave the city for! On over 6.5 (predominantly pastoral) acres, the country style home is immaculate and features 4 bedrooms or 3 with home office/study which has its own entrance. The Master Bedroom has a walk in robe and stylish new ensuite with granite bench top and spa, the further 2 spacious bedrooms have built in robes & all have bay windows which welcome an abundance of natural light. The new kitchen offers gorgeous views over the property and has beautiful cabinetry and granite bench tops, new 2 drawer dishwasher, 900mm stainless gas stove with electric oven and overlooks the dining and family room which has a split system for comfort all year round. Or maybe you could relax on the undercover rear entertaining deck and enjoy the serenity. There is also a huge formal lounge room with large wood heater (which is ducted) providing warmth enough for the whole home. Outside is a man's dream with a huge 12m x 8m machinery shed with power, a 6m x 6m workshop with mezzanine, a high roof double carport, perfect for the caravan or boat, a further storage shed, a wood shed, a large chook house, 2 dams and 7 fenced paddocks in all including an orchard and natural bush area. For the gardener there are lovely established gardens and there is an outdoor entertaining gazebo complete with built sink for entertaining your jealous city friends. Other features include automatic solar powered gate, ample water storage, 7 panel solar, ducted vacuum, a fruit orchard and a watering system for the garden. You will be captivated by this home!

Description:
Resort Living on 4 Flat Acres!
This fantastic lifestyle property on approximately 4 flat usable acres has everything for the whole family to enjoy. The house has been beautifully built to exacting standards and designed with the growing family in mind, with zoned areas so parents and kids can have their own space. The home has 5 spacious bedrooms, all with walk in robes and a study, the Master at the front of the home with a huge, sleek white bathroom and walk in robe. Also in this zone you will find the formal lounge and 2nd bedroom. The kitchen is central and has granite bench tops and stainless appliances and opens to the meals area and family room with cosy wood heater. From here you are led to the remaining 3 bedrooms, 2 of which share an ensuite bathroom and overlook the landscaped pool; what a teenagers dream! You then come to the huge games room with cathedral ceiling, slow combustion wood heater and it is big enough for a full sized billiard table and more, complete with a wet bar. Aside from the beautiful pool which is solar heated, other outdoor features include undercover entertaining, a natural gas fired heated spa and your very own sauna, perfect for getting rid of those aches and pains from a hard days work. This property really does have it all including a massive 18 x 15m shed which is plumbed with mains water for washing up as well as a wood heater for warmth while you are working and a 5 x 8m shed, both are concreted and have phone lines connected and power. As well as this there is a double lockup garage with remote providing undercover access to the home. The property backs onto the State Forest for privacy and the gardens and lawn are manicured and flat, which is rare for the hills & there is also a bus stop out the front for convenience. This home has too many features to list them all, make an appointment today to inspect and you wont be disappointed.

Description:
LIFESTYLE PROPERTY ON OVER 2 ACRES
A new and exciting lifestyle awaits the potential owners of this truly unique home in Cockatoo. Set on over 2 acres of stunning bushland and low maintenance gardens, this impressive home made from South Australian sandstone and featuring picture perfect vistas from every room, makes coming home to this property a pure delight.
Featuring 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, its the perfect home for a growing family with plenty of entertaining space.
You will delight at the feature bar, positioned in the centre of a pavilion style open plan living zone. Entertain guests either inside or outside with an impressive Al fresco area that will comfortably cater for many memorable celebrations and occasions. For those who require their own creative space for personal pursuits or would like the flexibility and privacy of working from home, there is a fabulous studio with separate entrance that suits all your home office needs. Other features of this stunning home include oversized doors and beautiful floor to ceiling windows allowing uninterrupted views. Dont miss an opportunity to experience living in this unique property

Description:
Make this Brand New Home Your Own
Perfectly located in a quiet no-through road close to Cockatoo’s shops and schools, this brand new home has great attention to detail and there is simply nothing to do. Featuring two large living areas, one of which opens onto a fantastic undercover deck with serene views over the surrounding neighbourhood, this home is ideally suited to those that want to enjoy life. Located on a manageable 1000m2 (approx.) block, there is plenty of parking with double garage plus workshop area and plenty of space to park additional vehicles. The modern kitchen is spacious with stainless steel appliances including dishwasher and large pantry. The large master bedroom features a modern full ensuite with double vanities and a walk in robe. The other 3 robed bedrooms are oversized plus there is a study nook or large storage cupboard. Additional features of this property include gas ducted heating and refrigerated cooling, 9 foot ceilings, polished spotted gum floorboards and water tank. This is a fantastic package which won’t last long – Call Mick Dolphin on 0429 684522, Meaghan Dolphin on 0422 578 114 or Amie Colbert on 0413 160 413 to arrange your inspection now. Due to strong market conditions please call before the open to confirm that it is still going ahead.

Description:
Almost New Home on an Acre!
What a fantastic opportunity; a great house and ideally located within walking distance to the Cockatoo shops, cafes, schools and transport, this Metricon built four bedroom family home has been beautifully finished and decorated with style. The exterior facade is an attractive mix of brick, render and timber giving the home character and it has a sealed driveway and low maintenance landscaped front garden. Inside is welcoming, light and bright and offers 4 bedrooms, 3 with built in robes and Master with walk in robe and gorgeous designer ensuite. There are two living areas, one makes an ideal formal lounge the other is a lovely family room and meals area which is adjacent to the stunning kitchen. The kitchen is beautifully appointed with stainless gas cooking, glass splash back and stone benchtops and overlooks the family room, or you can watch the kids play in the back yard whilst whipping up a feast. There is a great sized laundry with storage and the family bathroom is fitted out in keeping with the ensuite. Outside there is a double automatic garage with internal access, large undercover entertaining deck, undercover spa, a barn with concrete floor, 3 phase power and room for six cars! There is plenty of cleared space for the kids to play and the property is fully fenced for safety. This is truly a quality property that has everything a family could want or need. Inspect today!
CALL TO ARRANGE A PRIVATE INSPECTION TODAY!
Aaron Day 0407 365 994

Description:
All You Could Ever Want On 1/2 An Acre!
Situated in a peaceful and private location on a park like setting of approximately 1/2 an acre is this meticulously maintained family home that has plenty of room for even the largest of families. The home features a very functional floorplan that has been designed to ensure everyone has their own space .Boasting
5 bedrooms, multiple living areas including a formal lounge and dining room with feature open fireplace, family and meals area that is overlooked by the stunning kitchen with 900ml stainless steel oven, stainless steel dishwasher and stone benchtops.
